# Mapping from locale prefix → (console keymap, XKB layout).
# Console keymap is for /etc/vconsole.conf (TTY recovery).
# XKB layout is for /etc/X11/xorg.conf.d/00-keyboard.conf (graphical sessions).
# Languages that use non-Latin scripts on Latin keyboards get "us" for console
# and a native XKB layout for graphical input method support.
